{'product_detail': {'id': 8174258061451, 'title': '"3D Portrait - Alexander" Hanging Haunted House Decoration', 'body_html': '<p class="made-to-order">Production on this product is booked up until October. This product will not ship until after October 2022.</p>\n\n<p>They say great art seems to jump right off the canvas and come to life. Well, this portrait of young Alexander isn\'t exactly a masterpiece, but it does seem to have a life of its own. Killed in a gruesome accident while only a lad, it seems Alex\'s tortured soul resides between worlds, caught in this painting done shortly before his demise. Every year, on the anniversary of his death, it seems to try and escape the painting.</p>\n<p>Add a fantastic work of macabre art to your haunted gallery with the Alexander portrait 3D prop from The Horror Dome. This foam and latex design is ready to hang, right out of the box. Measuring 26" x 18" and 12" deep, this amazing prop is perfect for getting your house in the holiday spirit around Halloween. Create a frightening backstory for this demonic dude, or let your visitors fill in the blanks with their own imagination. Hang him up with other possessed paintings and create a ghastly waiting area for guests as they wait to enter your attraction. Draw attention to your place of business, or get your bar ready for the costume party, with this freaky fellow.</p>\n<p><i>Latex and foam prop is approx. 26 in. x 18 in. x 12 inches deep and is ready to hang.</i></p>', 'vendor': 'Distortions', 'product_type': 'Decorations', 'created_at': '2026-05-05T10:10:17-04:00', 'handle': '3d-portrait-alexander-hanging-haunted-house-decoration', 'updated_at': '2026-05-06T11:00:55-04:00', 'published_at': '2026-05-05T10:10:17-04:00', 'template_suffix': None, 'published_scope': 'global', 'tags': 'Child, Ghosts & Ghouls, Hanging, Haunted House Decor, Wall Art', 'status': 'active', 'admin_graphql_api_id': 'gid://shopify/Product/8174258061451', 'variants': [{'id': 46848558399627, 'product_id'